columns.name: Borough
columns.description: The borough in which the restaurant or food service establishment is located.

columns.name: RestaurantName
columns.description: The name of the restaurant or food service establishment

columns.name: SeatingChoice
columns.description: The type of seating for which the restaurant or food service establishment is configured for.

columns.name: LegalBusinessName
columns.description: The business name as registered with the NYC Department of Consumer Affairs (DCA).

columns.name: BusinessAddress
columns.description: The address of the restaurant or food service establishment.

columns.name: RestaurantInspectionID
columns.description: The unique ID that references the restaurant.

columns.name: IsSidewayCompliant
columns.description: Indicates if the restaurant or food service establishment located on the sidewalk is compliant with the Open Restaurants sidewalk requirements. Please note that “Sidewalk” and “Sideway” are interchangeable terms.

columns.name: IsRoadwayCompliant
columns.description: This is to validate if this restaurant is compliant for roadways.

columns.name: SkippedReason
columns.description: The reason a restaurant or food service establishment inspection was skipped

columns.name: InspectedOn
columns.description: The date and time of the inspection.

columns.name: AgencyCode
columns.description: City agency code.

columns.name: Postcode
columns.description: ZIP code of the restaurant.
